Class RasterInfo

java.lang.Object
  oracle.spatial.georaster.RasterInfo

public class RasterInfo
extends java.lang.Object

RasterInfo is a Java class mapped to the XML element RasterInfo in the Oracle Spatial GeoRaster metadata.
